==詞源==

本亞科命名自[[玲花蕉屬|玲花蕉屬]]（''Nolina''），而該屬的拉丁文則為了紀念[[法國|法國]]植物學家P·C·諾林（P. C. Nolin）<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/404980|title=Flora Boreali-Americana: Sistens Caracteres Plantarum Quas in America Septentrionali Collegit Et Detexit Andreas Michaux, vol. 1|last=Michaux|first=André|date=1803|publisher=Apud fratres Levrault,|year=|isbn=0665477570|location=Parisiis et Argentorati [i.e. Paris et Strasbourg, France] :|pages=207–208|language=|chapter=''Nolina''|doi=10.5962/bhl.title.50919|access-date=2018-04-29|archive-date=2018-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013125627/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/404980|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

